* {{flag|Ecuador|size=23px}}<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.asambleanacional.gob.ec/documentos/constitucion_de_bolsillo.pdf|title=Articles 1, 11, 26, and 66.8 of the Ecuadorian Constitution|accessdate=2019-12-19|archive-date=2015-08-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150813100049/http://www.asambleanacional.gob.ec/documentos/constitucion_de_bolsillo.pdf|dead-url=no}}</ref>
* {{flag|Paraguay|size=23px}}
* {{flag|Peru|size=23px}}<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.tc.gob.pe/legconperu/constitucion.html|title=Article 50° of the Peruvian Constitution|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20070324043856/http://www.tc.gob.pe/legconperu/constitucion.html|archivedate=2007-03-24|accessdate=2019-12-19|dead-url=no}}</ref>
* {{flag|Uruguay|size=23px}}<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.refworld.org/cgi-bin/texis/vtx/rwmain?page=category&category=LEGAL&publisher=&type=&coi=URY&docid=3ae6b5600&skip=0|title=Constitution of the Oriental Republic of Uruguay, Chapter III, Article 5.|accessdate=2019-12-19|archive-date=2015-11-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151117015548/http://www.refworld.org/cgi-bin/texis/vtx/rwmain?page=category&category=LEGAL&publisher=&type=&coi=URY&docid=3ae6b5600&skip=0|dead-url=no}}</ref>
